# type: Content of: <chapter><section><title>
#: en/installing.dbk:317
msgid "Popularity contest"
msgstr "流行度统计"

# type: Content of: <chapter><section><para>
#: en/installing.dbk:319
msgid ""
"The installation system will again offer to install the <systemitem role="
"\"package\">popularity-contest</systemitem> package.  This package was not "
"installed by default in &oldreleasename; but it was installed in older "
"releases."
msgstr ""
"安装环境会再次提供<systemitem role=\"package\">popularity-contest</"
"systemitem>软件包的安装选项。在&oldreleasename;版中这个软件包默认状态是不安装"
"的，而在早期版本中是要安装的。"

# type: Content of: <chapter><section><para>
#: en/installing.dbk:324
msgid ""
"<systemitem role=\"package\">popularity-contest</systemitem> provides the "
"Debian project with valuable information on which packages in the "
"distribution are actually used.  This information is used mainly to decide "
"the order in which packages are included on installation CD-ROMs, but is "
"also often consulted by Debian developers in deciding whether or not to "
"adopt a package that no longer has a maintainer."
msgstr ""
"<systemitem role=\"package\">popularity-contest</systemitem>向Debian项目提供"
"了关于发布中哪些软件包被实际使用的宝贵信息。这些信息主要用于决定哪些软件包应"
"当被包含在安装光盘上，而Debian开发人员也常查看它们以决定要不要采用不再有维护"
"者的软件包。"

# type: Content of: <chapter><section><para>
#: en/installing.dbk:332
msgid ""
"Information from <systemitem role=\"package\">popularity-contest</"
"systemitem> is processed anonymously.  We would appreciate it if you would "
"participate in this official survey, helping to improve Debian."
msgstr ""
"<systemitem role=\"package\">popularity-contest</systemitem>的信息收集过程是"
"匿名进行的。如果您能参与这项调查，帮我们改进Debian，我们会非常高兴。"

# type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#~ msgid "No reboot during the installation"
#~ msgstr "请避免在安装过程中重启"

# type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#~ msgid ""
#~ "Previously, the installation was split into two parts: setting up the "
#~ "base system and making it bootable, followed by a reboot and after that "
#~ "the execution of <command>base-config</command> which would take care of "
#~ "things like user setup, setup of the package management system and "
#~ "installation of additional packages (using tasksel)."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "原先，安装过程被分为两个部分：设置基本系统并使之可以启动，然后重启并在执行"
#~ "命令<command>base-config</command>（它将完成诸如用户设置等内容）后，进行软"
#~ "件包管理器的设置以及额外软件包的安装等（使用命令tasksel）。"

# type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#~ msgid ""
#~ "For &releasename; the second stage has been integrated into Debian "
#~ "Installer itself.  This has a number of advantages, including increased "
#~ "security and the fact that after the reboot at the end of the "
#~ "installation the new system should already have the correct timezone and, "
#~ "if you installed the Desktop environment, will at once start the "
#~ "graphical user interface."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "%releasename;的第二阶段已经被并入Debian安装程序里了。这样做有很多好处，包"
#~ "括安全性的提高，还有当新系统安装结束并重启后，时区已经设置好了，而且如果您"
#~ "安装了桌面环境，还会立即启动图形用户界面。"

# type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#~ msgid "UTF-8 encoding default for new systems"
#~ msgstr "新安装的操作系统默认编码为UTF-8"

# type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#~ msgid ""
#~ "The installer will set up systems to use UTF-8 encoding rather than the "
#~ "old language-specific encodings (like ISO-8859-1, EUC-JP or KOI-8)."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "安装程序会将系统编码优先设置为UTF-8，而不是早期的语言编码（如ISO-8859-1,"
#~ "EUC-JP或KOI-8）。"

# type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#~ msgid "Cryptographic verification of downloaded packages"
#~ msgstr "已下载软件包的密码验证"

# type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#~ msgid ""
#~ "Packages downloaded with the installer are now cryptographically checked "
#~ "using <command>apt</command>, making it more difficult to compromise a "
#~ "system being installed over the network."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "现在，安装程序下载的软件包需要经由命令<command>apt</command>进行密码验证，"
#~ "这使得通过网络安装操作系统的过程更难被破坏。"
